000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1t T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn trong n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Duy M\u1ea1nh khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 chia l\u00e0m hai n\u1eeda, m\u1ed9t b\u00ean cho r\u1eb1ng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y th\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng, b\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 CLB HAGL kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-ha-noi-vs-hagl-19h00-ngay-54-vleague-2018-372-183576.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL</span></span> tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 0-5, HAGL c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tam the do cua Tang Tien sau cu dap vao dau goi cua Duy Manh la buoc ngoat cua tran dau.\" title=\"T\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/tranh-cai-quanh-viec-bau-duc-phat-tang-tien-vi-dap-vao-chan-duy-manh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1t T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn tr\u00ean trang fanpage c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1t T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 1 c\u1ee7a V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00e1n th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c r\u0103n \u0111e \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ea1n b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c s\u00e2n c\u1ecf t\u1ea1i V-League ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t. T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n <em>Gia Hi\u1ec7u</em> \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: &quot;Nh\u00ecn \u1edf s\u00e2n r\u00f5, xa n\u1eeda s\u00e2n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1p ng\u01b0\u1eddi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n <em>Hoang Thanh</em> nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;Ngon nh\u01b0ng x\u1eed l\u00fd n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 hay h\u01a1n l\u00e0 post l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng&quot;. T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n <em>Ho\u00e0ng Duy</em> c\u0169ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c: &quot;Ri\u00eang c\u00e1i n\u00e0y th\u00ec \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9. \u0110\u00e1 nh\u01b0 gi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Pha \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 pha ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng r\u1ed3i. Ng\u1ed3i h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00e0 ngh\u0129 c\u00f2n g\u00ec n\u1eefa&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn kh\u00e1c cho r\u1eb1ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean, b\u1edfi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF x\u1eed l\u00fd. D\u00f9 sao \u0111i n\u1eefa, c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 c\u0169ng n\u00ean b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd ra \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00f3ng ng\u1ecdn gi\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n <em>T\u1ed1ng T\u00f9ng Giang</em> nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;N\u1eb7ng nh\u1ec3. C\u1ea5m \u0111\u00f4i ba tr\u1eadn l\u00e0 kinh l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i, c\u1ea5m nguy\u00ean l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i lu\u00f4n&quot;. T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n <em>L\u00e2m T\u00f9ng</em> vi\u1ebft: &quot;Ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng qu\u00e1. C\u1ea5m hai tr\u1eadn th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n <em>Nguy\u1ec5n V\u00e2n Trang</em> k\u00eau g\u1ecdi HAGL gi\u1ea3m \u00e1n: &quot;D\u00f9 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn l\u00e0 b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng BHL k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt h\u1ebft giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 1 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng cho anh \u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-291-183608.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-291-183608.html\">\u0102n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t C\u1ef0C N\u1eb6NG</span><br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 n\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"836","checkdouble":"183617"},{"date":"19:23 05/04","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/4: Willian \u0111\u1ebfn MU thay Mata","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-54-willian-den-mu-thay-mata.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{b