p \u0111\u1ea3o. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ch\u1ec9 trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wenger-lacazette-khong-con-la-chinh-minh-sau-khi-den-arsenal-172-183574.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Alexandre Lacazette</span></span> v\u00e0 Aaron Ramsey m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 c\u1ee7a &quot;ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thang dam CSKA Moscow, HLV Wenger keu goi Arsenal khong chu quan hinh anh\" title=\"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CSKA Moscow, HLV Wenger k\u00eau g\u1ecdi Arsenal kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/thang-dam-cska-moscow-hlv-wenger-keu-goi-arsenal-khong-duoc-chu-quan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Wenger k\u00eau g\u1ecdi Arsenal gi\u1eef s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCSKA Moscow ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Golovin, ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u1ecfi cho hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n VEB Arena. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Wenger v\u1eabn k\u00eau g\u1ecdi Arsenal ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o b\u1edfi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. H\u1ed3i n\u0103m 2006 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League, Arsenal t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CSKA Moscow tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Arsenal ph\u1ea3i t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac&quot; - HLV Wenger k\u00eau g\u1ecdi Arsenal: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cao \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i. Arsenal ch\u01b0a v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng HLV Wenger kh\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng CSKA l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Golovin l\u00e0 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh, gi\u00fap Arsenal ch\u01a1i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Wenger cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 CSKA Moscow l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt cao v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ea5t nhanh. H\u1ecd g\u00e2y ra cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t linh ho\u1ea1t, th\u00f4ng minh&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Arsenal 4-1 CSKA Moscow\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 4-1 CSKA Moscow\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/Thong-so-Arsenal-4-1-CSKA.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 4-1 CSKA Moscow</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-arsenal-vs-cska-moscow-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718-372-183606.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/truc-tiep-arsenal-vs-cska-moscow-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-arsenal-vs-cska-moscow-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718-372-183606.html\">Arsenal 4-1 CSKA Moscow: Th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u1ed7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Arsene Wenger \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh trong cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League \u0111\u00eam qua. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft g\u1ecdn nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nN.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"833","checkdouble":"183613"},{"date":"06:28 06/04","title":"T\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0 Man Utd: Europa League gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a ng\