fy;\"><strong>Khi Arsenal theo b\u01b0\u1edbc Man Utd</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Man Utd c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 t\u1ea1i Premier League, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Champions League 2017-18</span></span>. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ajax tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Friends Arena gi\u00fap &quot;qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; nghi\u1ec5m nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tu Arsenal va Man Utd Europa League gio la cua nguoi Anh hinh anh\" title=\"T\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0 Man Utd Europa League gi\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/ars-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Arsenal v\u00e0 Man Utd \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i Europa League \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 Champions League.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd th\u00ec Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111i tr\u00ean \u0111\u00fang con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, &quot;ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7&quot; nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6, gi\u1ed1ng Man Utd n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. C\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea1ng hai ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Arsene Wenger ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-arsenal-vs-cska-moscow-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718-372-183606.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">\u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i CSKA Moscow v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-1</span></span> \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. S\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ai c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y khi Arsenal ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 CSKA Moscow, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1eadc trung t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Arsene Wenger sau tr\u1eadn c\u00e0ng cho th\u1ea5y Europa League quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Arsenal. Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn 4-1 nh\u01b0ng &quot;gi\u00e1o s\u01b0&quot; v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 &quot;b\u1eadt&quot; l\u1ea1i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Wenger th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ed1ng Jose Mourinho m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, &quot;ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&quot; kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Europa League l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a &quot;qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League l\u00e0 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 Arsenal v\u00e0 Man Utd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf &quot;m\u00e2m tr\u00ean&quot; Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Europa League gi\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh?</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea7n \u0111a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf top 5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi Europa League, khi h\u1ecd ho\u1eb7c t\u1eadp trung cho Champions League, ho\u1eb7c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 4. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Atletico Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111e d\u1ecda ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Arsene Wenger.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man Utd vo dich Europa League mua truoc.\" title=\"Man Utd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/mu-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Man Utd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Diego Simeone ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111ao to b\u00faa l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 Europa League, b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n&nbsp;Atletico ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau khi n\u1eb1m trong top 4 La Liga. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi, trong khi Arsenal ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi 120% s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u00f4ng quan d\u1ef1 c\u00fap C1 m\u00f9a sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0 Man Utd, ai c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y Europa League c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &quot;l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ecba&quot; c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Premier League. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn tranh nhau 4 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1ef1 Champions League, hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u00f4ng qua ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea1ng hai ch\u00e2u \u00c2u sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m Big Six c\u1ee7a Premier League. Sau tr\u1eadn thua Arsenal, HLV Gennaro Gattuso t\u1eebng l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u ngao ng\u00e1n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf. N\u00ean nh\u1edb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/ac-milan-1467.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">AC Milan</span></span> kh\u00f4ng y\u1ebfu nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f3 s\u00e1nh ngang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t. Li\u1ec7u sang n\u0103m, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn The Blues ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Arsenal 4-1 CSKA Moscow\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 4-1 CSKA Moscow\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/Thong-so-Arsenal-4-1-CSKA.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 4-1 CSKA Moscow</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-arsenal-vs-cska-moscow-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718-372-183606.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/truc-tiep-arsenal-vs-cska-moscow-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-arsenal-vs-cska-moscow-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718-372-183606.html\">Arsenal 4-1 CSKA Moscow: Th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u1ed7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Arsene Wenger \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh trong cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League \u0111\u00eam qua. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft g\u1ecdn nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<st