l,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tin vui cho HLV Jose Mourinho: Fabinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Monaco \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ecfa nguy\u1ec7n.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd The Sun, Fabinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn MU trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng h\u1eadu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 v\u00e0 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Monaco c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Monaco s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i ngai v\u00e0ng Ligue 1 cho PSG (k\u00e9m 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc 7 v\u00f2ng cu\u1ed1i). \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Fabinho v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hau ve Fabinho muon den MU trong tuong lai hinh anh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Fabinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn MU trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/hau-ve-fabinho-muon-den-mu-trong-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Fabinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn MU v\u00e0 r\u1eddi Monaco<br>\r\n            </span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, Fabinho \u01b0u ti\u00ean M.U nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Monaco sau khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u201ch\u00fat m\u00e1u\u201d t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c. Monaco hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Fabinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 c\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. M.U hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa thay th\u1ebf Michael Carrick v\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini s\u1ebd ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Fabinho, M.U c\u0169ng nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Jean Michael-Seri c\u1ee7a Nice v\u00e0 Fred c\u1ee7a Shakhtar Donetsk. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Fabinho v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1edfi x\u00e9t tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Carrick v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Nemanja Matic \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-mu-mua-willian-thay-mata-172-183571.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Ng\u00f4i sao thay th\u1ebf Mata t\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tiet-lo-ibrahimovic-khong-sang-trung-quoc-vi-ly-do-nay-172-183496.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Ibrahimovic ch\u00ea 100 tri\u1ec7u USD t\u1eeb Trung Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-cho-mu-hoac-chelsea-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-183449.html\">Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alderweireld cho MU ho\u1eb7c Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuo